content: During the second quarter, we completed Phase 1 of the Castle Peak compressor station, which added 160 million cubic feet a day of compression capacity in the liquids rich midstream corridor in Tyler and Wetzel counties. It was a tremendous quarter from a strategic and financial standpoint in AM we acquired strategic photon assets that add several years to the underlying inventory dedicated to AM and we direct the business model by transitioning to generating consistent, repeatable free cash flow after dividends.
